 TALK

 July 8 at Ramakrishna Mission Institute of Culture, Shivananda Hall; 6 pm: Dr Sitanath Goswami will speak in Sanskrit on Bhagavad-Gita. 

 WORKSHOP

 July 8 at Marudhara, 6 Merlin Park; 6 pm - 7 pm: Marudhara presents an intensive first level workshop on classical aerobics, an experimental creative work pioneered by Kathak choreographer Nandini Sinha. The introductory class (July 8) is free for all participants. The actual workshop comprises 12 classes of one hour each beginning July 9. Details at (11 am - 5 pm). 

